#HOME
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>
body {
  background-color: lightgreen;
}
 
h1 {
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
}
 
p {
  font-family: verdana;
  font-size: 40px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
 
<h1>Mi primer codigo de css</h1>
<p>hola.</p>
 
</body>
</html>
 
 
 
 
